<mjml>
  <mj-include path="./head.mjml" />
  <mj-body mj-class="body">
    <mj-wrapper background-color="#F0F0F0">
      <mj-section />
      <mj-section css-class="section">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text mj-class="headline"
            >You have received an application from ${menteeFullName}!</mj-text
          >
          <mj-divider mj-class="divider-top" css-class="divider" />

          <mj-text mj-class="text" padding="0 0 20px 0"
            >Hi ${mentorName},</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >You have received a mentee application from ${menteeFullName} from
            ${locationNameFormatted}!
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Please log into ReDI Connect to review this application as soon as
            you find the time.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Once you’ve checked their profile and message to you and you do
            want to become their mentor: that’s great! You can then accept their application and get in touch. Please make
            sure to already suggest a date and time for a first meeting, whether
            it be online or in person.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-image
            src="https://redi-connect-email-assets.s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/review-application.png"
            align="left"
            padding="10px 0 30px 0"
            target="_blank"
            width="250px"
            href="${loginUrl}"
          />
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >If, upon checking their profile and message to you, you realize
            that you cannot support them in the way they are looking for, please
            kindly decline their application and make sure to send them a quick
            message to explain why.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Should the reason be that you are too busy to take on a mentorship
            right now, remember that you can always set your mentee count
            capacity to ‘0’ in your profile - then you won’t be visible to any
            mentees until you change this back.</mj-text
          >

          <mj-text mj-class="text">All the best,</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text">Your ReDI Career Support Team</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-include path="./footer.career.support.team.mjml" />
      <mj-section />
    </mj-wrapper>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
